  <h2>Subscribe Text</h2>

  <div class="content"><div class='orange-text'>
<a href="https://secure.readersdigest.ca/subscription/bh/2011/01-39/subscribe.php?partner=201101_bh_website_header_textlink" rel="nofollow">Subscribe to Best Health Magazine today and save over 55% off the cover price!</a></div></div>
