				<div class="img"><a href="/eat-well/nutrition/9-arthritis-fighting-superfoods/"><img src="/sites/default/files/images/arthritis-hands.teaser.jpg" class = 'imgbrd_block' alt = '9 arthritis-fighting superfoods'/></a></div>
				<div class="cont"><h2><a href="/eat-well/nutrition/9-arthritis-fighting-superfoods/">9 arthritis-fighting superfoods</a></h2><p>Ease achy joints with the nutrients from these superfoods<span class="more-arrow"><a href="#"> &raquo;</a></span></p></div>
